snippet.title: New You Media
snippet.description:
New You, the voice of health and beauty, redefines the traditional women’s consumer magazine with cutting edge health, wellness, fashion, anti-aging, and beauty news. New You is thought provoking and stylish, filled with exclusive celebrity interviews, the latest trends in skincare and aesthetic procedures, nutrition, fitness, and much more.

Subscribe to the magazine at www.NewYou.com/Subscribe or subscribe to our YouTube channel for the latest videos with behind the scenes celebrity cover photoshoots. Peek behind the scenes of our sexy photo shoot with cover girl, Sharon Stone. Our past covers featured Courteney Cox, Martha Stewart, Sharon Stone, Kris Jenner, Brooke Burke, Robin McGraw, Jenny McCarthy, Brooke Shields, Carmen Dell’Orefice, Daisy Fuentes and many more.  Visit www.newyou.com often for exclusive celebrity interviews, health and beauty tips and the latest in nutrition and fitness.
